2) Pipe 단면 치수표												
												
		외경 D (mm)	내경 d (mm)	단면적 A (mm^2)	관성모멘트 Ix (mm^4)	관성모멘트 Iy (mm^4)	회전반경 rx (mm)	회전반경 ry (mm)	단면계수 Zx (mm^3)	단면계수 Zy (mm^3)		
	300A PIPE	318.5	304.7	=PI()*(C14^2-D14^2)/4	=PI()*(C14^4-D14^4)/64	=PI()*(C14^4-D14^4)/64	=SQRT(F14/E14)	=SQRT(G14/E14)	=PI()*(C14^4-D14^4)/(32*C14)	=PI()*(C14^4-D14^4)/(32*C14)		
	250A PIPE (#60)	267.4	242	=PI()*(C15^2-D15^2)/4	=PI()*(C15^4-D15^4)/64	=PI()*(C15^4-D15^4)/64	=SQRT(F15/E15)	=SQRT(G15/E15)	=PI()*(C15^4-D15^4)/(32*C15)	=PI()*(C15^4-D15^4)/(32*C15)		
	400A PIPE (#40)	406.4	381	=PI()*(C16^2-D16^2)/4	=PI()*(C16^4-D16^4)/64	=PI()*(C16^4-D16^4)/64	=SQRT(F16/E16)	=SQRT(G16/E16)	=PI()*(C16^4-D16^4)/(32*C16)	=PI()*(C16^4-D16^4)/(32*C16)		
	400A PIPE (#60)	406.4	373	=PI()*(C17^2-D17^2)/4	=PI()*(C17^4-D17^4)/64	=PI()*(C17^4-D17^4)/64	=SQRT(F17/E17)	=SQRT(G17/E17)	=PI()*(C17^4-D17^4)/(32*C17)	=PI()*(C17^4-D17^4)/(32*C17)		
												
												
